OL,6,FA giant red and blue sign hangs above
OL,7,Freception: "City of Sanctuary." This
OL,8,Fis the home of Asylum Link, a charity
OL,9,Fsupporting asylum seekers and
OL,10,Frefugees. Here people find food,
OL,11,Ffriendship, help and information while
OL,12,Fthey await their fate.
OL,14,FI spent a few days here at the end of
OL,15,FMay and start of June.
