OL,6,FIn February last year, protests
OL,7,Foutside the Suites Hotel in Knowsley
OL,8,Fwhere asylum seekers were being housed
OL,9,Fdescended into violence, with attacks
OL,10,Fon police officers and a police van
OL,11,Fbeing set on hire.
OL,13,FEarlier this year, eight men were
OL,14,Fconvicted of violent disorder.
OL,16,FEwan Roberts, who runs Asylum Link,
OL,17,Fsaid he was shocked by the level of
OL,18,Fviolence shown that night, but said
OL,19,Fthe asylum system breeds "resentment"
OL,20,Fand "fear" in the local population.
