OL,3,CNo easy answers: Britain's immigration
OL,4,Cdilemma
OL,6,FBoth the Conservatives and Labour have
OL,7,Fvowed to bring down levels of
OL,8,Fimmigration if elected, but neither
OL,9,Fhave set out how they would improve
OL,10,Fproductivity in the long term with
OL,11,Ffewer people arriving.
OL,13,FReform UK argue that net migration
OL,14,Fshould be zero - to allow the UK to
OL,15,Fimprove access to the NHS, housing and
OL,16,Fother public services for the current
OL,17,Fpopulation.
